node.text: 2017 playoffs in Calgary with the Budweiser team.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021 tagging @nhlcollection. May be an image of 10 people and text.

node.text: NFL x NHL comparisons created by @nhlcollection. What do you think?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'nolan bianchi @nolanbianchi Steve Yzerman on the Alex Nedeljkovic trade: "You're going to have to ask them why they were comfortable doing that." #LGRW HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Even Stevie knew he fleeced the Canes 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SIGNED NEW YORK RANGERS BARCLAY GOODROW YEARS, $21.6M ($3.6M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE LA'.

node.text: Barclay Goodrow has officially signed his six-year deal with the Rangers.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'TRADE HOCKEY COLLECTIVE 5 BaV SPE RECEIVES 3 RECEIVES SHAYNE GOSTISBEHERE 2ND ROUND PICK 7TH ROUND PICK'.

node.text: The Flyers get cap relief for Shayne Ghostisbehere.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021. May be an image of ‎text that says '‎TRADE RECEIVES ALEX NEDELJKOVIC CANE RECEIVES םOOS JONATHAN BERNIER 3RD ROUND PICK / PIERRE LEBRUN HOCKEY COLLECTIVE‎'‎.

node.text: The Red Wings have acquired Alex Nedeljkovic from the Hurricanes and signed him to a two-year, $6M deal ($3M AAV).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, playing hockey and text that says 'SIGNED OILERS Gilers Oilers MIKE SMITH 41 2 YEARS, $4.4M ($2.2M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: 39 year old Mike Smith gets a two-year deal from the Oilers.

node.text: The Kraken’s new goaltender, Chris Dreidger.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SIGNED S JAMIE OLEKSIAK 5 YEARS, $23M ($4.6M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE C'.

node.text: Jamie Oleksiak gets a five-year deal from the Kraken. He will be their pick from the Stars tonight.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, playing hockey and text that says 'SIGNED $ y A ADAM LARSSON QILERS YEARS, $16M ($4M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: The Kraken have signed UFA Adam Larsson to a four-year deal. He will be their pick from the Oilers tonight.
